INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS: Head to your Steam folder. Then follow down through SteamApps
=>Counterstrike-source=>cstrike=>maps and unzip/extract both files named fy_cuba in the 
maps folder.

BUGs: Under one of the windows there is some black artifacting going on. Easy to ignore. :p

Enjoy!
